Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.13,0:02:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Nora] Here, kitty kitty!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.01,0:03:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.25,0:03:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- Head to the nearest shelter!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.09,0:03:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- Those shelters are gonna fill up soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.15,0:03:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- They're all we've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.42,0:03:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We just have to hold off the Grimm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.99,0:03:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- Okay, yes sir, understood, over and out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.87,0:03:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- New orders?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.80,0:03:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.82,0:04:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- Take us to Atlas, we\Nwon't survive down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.02,0:04:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- Why isn't Ironwood doing anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.90,0:04:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- Please, everyone. We're doing our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.97,0:04:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We will get you to safety.\NJust give us a little more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.37,0:04:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- Atlas, Mantle, I know you're scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.54,0:04:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here with General Ironwood,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.58,0:04:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and we have a message for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.98,0:04:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What he has to say may sound unbelievable,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.32,0:04:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,but it is all true.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.46,0:04:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- An ancient and terrible evil lies\Noutside of our kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.53,0:04:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It was responsible for\Nthe destruction of Beacon,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.83,0:04:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,the attack on Haven, and for\Nthe recent attacks on Mantle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.33,0:04:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This powerful force goes\Nby the name of Salem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.84,0:04:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- He's doing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.38,0:04:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Ironwood] Salem\Nseeks only to divide us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.81,0:04:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- To turn us against each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.65,0:04:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- If she can incite hatred in us,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.98,0:05:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we will lure in the Grimm,\Nand destroy ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.96,0:05:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Robyn] Salem herself does\Nnot work alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.03,0:05:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Her minions have invaded our very city.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.70,0:05:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Ironwood] Arthur\NWatts and Tyrian Callows.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.40,0:05:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,These men are the ones responsible
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.40,0:05:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,for the recent murders in Mantle,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.17,0:05:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and for sabotaging the heating grid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.20,0:05:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But we cannot let ourselves\Ngive in to fear and panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.11,0:05:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That is what she wants!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.58,0:05:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead, we must unite,\Nand fight back, together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.62,0:05:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Every single one of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.42,0:05:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- Alright, single file line!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.49,0:05:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Place a hand on the shoulder in front of you,\Neyes forward, move, move, move!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.13,0:05:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Show them how it's done, kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.56,0:05:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- Where did you learn to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.20,0:05:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- Morning school route?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.07,0:05:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Ironwood] This, my\Nfriends, is why I was forced
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.24,0:05:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,to divert resources from Mantle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.44,0:05:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,For the Amity Communication Tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.34,0:05:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Amity Tower is now completed,\Nand ready to launch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.78,0:06:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It will re-establish all\Nglobal communications--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.78,0:06:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- The Colosseum remodeling\Nwas a communications tower?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.85,0:06:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,How did James get this past me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.82,0:06:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Ironwood] The council and I have decided
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.32,0:06:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,to evacuate everyone in Mantle to Atlas.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.66,0:06:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I am withdrawing all defenses from Amity
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.89,0:06:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to assist with\Nrepelling the Grimm in Mantle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.23,0:06:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- We must put aside our differences
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.50,0:06:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and band together to defeat this threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.00,0:06:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I fully support General Ironwood's plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.45,0:06:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- The Grimm should have\Ndestroyed our enemies,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.92,0:06:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,not made them friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.08,0:06:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- Wait, our tin soldier's\Nheart has cost him his mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.09,0:06:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to keep their attention on Mantle
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.82,0:06:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,for as long as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.56,0:06:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- You want more chaos\Nthan a Grimm invasion?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.00,0:06:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- If anyone on Remnant could deliver that,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.13,0:06:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,wouldn't it be you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.20,0:06:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Robyn] If you've made it to your\Nlocal shelter, stay put.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.34,0:07:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Help is on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.34,0:07:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And for those of you in Sector 17,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.51,0:07:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be seeing you personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.58,0:07:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- Come to think of it, I do have an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.62,0:07:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Cinder] I still can't believe\Nthose idiots beat us here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.35,0:07:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Vacuo was supposed to be the next target.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.36,0:07:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The timeline has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.16,0:07:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You said the farm boy has the lamp?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.63,0:07:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Find him, take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.00,0:07:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we get what I need first!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.00,0:07:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we get what we want, now go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.91,0:07:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ironwood's been hiding the\NWinter Maiden for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.88,0:07:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonight I'm going to find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.75,0:07:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The general's as\Npredictable as his androids.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.32,0:07:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Threaten what he has, and\Nhe'll flock to protect it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.74,0:08:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- Get in, get in!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.46,0:08:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- I've got this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.78,0:08:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- Alright, we just need
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.14,0:08:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,to get everyone to the closest air pad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.08,0:08:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- The closest LZ is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.29,0:08:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- There.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.04,0:09:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- Penny, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.61,0:10:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ouch, those tusks sure are dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.45,0:10:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- They sure are.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.79,0:10:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I have a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.23,0:10:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.94,0:10:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Penny] Over here, you big bag of bones!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.07,0:10:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Ruby] Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.06,0:11:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yeah, they saved us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.39,0:11:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Woman In Crowd] The\Nprotector of Mantle!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.77,0:11:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Yang] Just sent the ship up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.07,0:11:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Heading to the next LZ.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.74,0:11:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Nora] Ditto.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.11,0:11:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Jaune] Same here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.91,0:11:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ms. Hill, the southern\Noutskirts are clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.94,0:11:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It should be safe to\Nbegin evacuations now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.98,0:11:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- Great work, Penny. Over and out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.58,0:11:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure you get these people to safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.58,0:11:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna check for any stragglers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.00,0:11:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- Robyn Hill, for such a little bird,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.00,0:11:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,you have quite the impact around here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.77,0:12:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Bringing hope and a smile wherever you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.71,0:12:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I find it... upsetting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.19,0:12:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- Sorry Callows, I really\Nwanted to pummel you on my own,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.56,0:12:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,but the general insisted I share.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.33,0:12:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- Well, you're not the\Nonly one with a grudge.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.00,0:12:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- You'll both have to get in line.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.46,0:13:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hmm... This will certainly do the trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.73,0:13:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Although I wouldn't\Nexactly call it finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.21,0:13:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Ironwood] Arthur Watts...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.91,0:13:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.78,0:13:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- It wasn't finished, it was bait.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.23,0:13:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- You know, James, this place has
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.29,0:13:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,always been a technological marvel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.50,0:13:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- Truly, even before you\Nwent and did all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.71,0:13:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The different types of\Ndust, the biome system,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.68,0:13:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and of course, everything that\Ngoes into controlling them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.62,0:14:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- You always were a pain in the ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.62,0:14:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- At the risk of sounding cliche, James,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.99,0:14:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't be going down without a fight.
